@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rrezpq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (1.00 + tmp)
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.cos((v1 + 0.93 * v0 + 0.52)))
    v2 = wp.cos((wp.cos(v2 + 0.08) + wp.abs(v1 + 0.97)))
    data[tid] = v0
